This song is based on folk tale of MARVI and Umar(king). Marvi was kidnapped by a king who forcefully wanted to marry her.But Marvi loved Khet and didn't marry king. At the end king had to release the Marvi and this song was sung by her clan on her arrival.
Thank me later. Enjoy the song.
